channel.description:
[b]IboPKZ - The new Project. Posting on Moparscape (A Pro Project on A noob Forum ;)
[b]Btw, lets start... Some information and pictures about my new project. And Ofcourse the download link -.-.
Donator Shops, from My client. Shop = Made by my self And only donators can acces this shop :). [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/2jb8vbd.jpg[/img][/img]
Here is the Donator place, made by my self and the place is coded by ibo. There is the donator shop. [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/iy1z86.jpg[/img][/img]
Working slayer, Click on the slayer icon and u tele to there. Talk to Vanneka and u get task. Complete it and u get much Slayer experience. [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/2nsalgx.jpg[/img][/img]
[b]Im not posting much more, pictures couse it sucks to upload it all. Here is some inportant information about the client.
[i]Working:[/i][/b]
[b]Vesta long working 100% D-claws working 100%
Go to status, and click on a skill and u get tele to the place where you can train it! Teleport is working 100% in ancient mage lunar mage, and normal magic spell book!
When you downloaded the client & source, extract it in your map and read the information tabs, about how to use.
Commands are working 100%, and to insert NPC go to the NPC.TXT Notepad. And look at the npc and the drop he has.
Lagg is fixed by TehNoobShow < The orginial :D. And the Admin & Mod icons is made by TehNoobWorld < The orginal :D.
This is my first Pro post on moparscape. You can find this post 2 on google.
DOWNLOAD LINK: http://uppit.com/v/Y4Z5DGFZ
SORRY WHEN PICTURES NOT WORKING.
(IboPKZ) My first project.
Read the notepads inside the client, for more information and contact.
Made by Ibo :cool:[/b]
